data.description: Beautiful two-level residence in Vail is the one you've been looking for! Explore inside to discover an impressive open layout featuring gleaming wood-look floor, soothing color palette, & modern recessed lighting. The spotless kitchen boasts white shaker cabinets adorned with crown moulding, a chic mosaic backsplash, stainless steel appliances, a pantry, & a center island equipped with a breakfast bar. You will find a spacious loft with a custom stacked stone fireplace and cabinetry, offering the perfect space for an additional living area! The primary bedroom showcases plush carpet in all the right places & a private bathroom with dual sinks. Fall in love with the large professionally landscaped backyard, including covered & open patios, ideal for evening relaxation or alfresco dining!
